<Base title="About — North Lane Pick" description="About North Lane Pick: curated skincare and SPF picks for US shoppers.">
  <h1>About North Lane Pick</h1>
  <p>
    North Lane Pick is a small curation site focused on one thing: helping US
    shoppers find skincare and sun-protection products that are actually worth
    buying. We write simple, practical guides — the correct order to apply your
    routine, how often to reapply SPF, and which lightweight sunscreens are worth
    your money.
  </p>
  <p>
    We don't manufacture or sell products ourselves. Instead, we point you to
    items available on Amazon and earn a small commission when you buy through our
    links, at no extra cost to you. See our
    <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">affiliate disclosure</a> for details.
  </p>
  <p>
    Have a question or a product you'd like us to cover? We're always refining our
    picks based on what readers find useful.
  </p>
</Base>
